    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "This is due to the fact that the old ABI decoder does not perform verification of inputs. The `invalid` you are seeing is because it comes from `a == Test.A`, a point where internal checking is done again right before the equality comparison. This will be fixed soon.",
